ime freeing the data needed to deliver business insights.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#454156" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][testimonial_slider style="default" autorotate="6500"][testimonial name=" Chief Architect at Global Financial Institution" quote="My assignment is to make the data more accessible and available, to accelerate speed to insight, yet at the same time be aware of the regulatory environment and the need for strong data governance. Other products we looked failed to address compliance requirements without significant downtime and performance constraints- NuCypher allows us to reduce our data risk and increase our business agility." id="1483382588028-2b3ff-516a" title="Testimonial" tab_id="1483386688434-7"][/testimonial][/testimonial_slider][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" text_align="left"][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#01579b" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390617043{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Encryption of Sensitive Data</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0277bd" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390762481{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Role-Based Access Control</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0288d1" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390774334{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Boundary Control</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner boxed="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#039be5" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390782689{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Key Management</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483391671638{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #28b1d3;">Encryption of Sensitive Data Everywhere It Goes</span></h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>End-to End Encryption of Sensitive Data</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]The NuCypher platform supports granular encryption, allowing fine-grained decryption permissions both for internal employees and external partners and customers. in multi-tenant cloud environments and centralized data lakes. And it works seamlessly across multi-tenant environments and centralized data lakes as well as on-premise and in private, hybrid, and public clouds.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483391684872{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #28b1d3;">Fine Grained Access Control</span></h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Role-Based Access Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This gives you the ability to maintain a separation of duties between administrative and authorized user access. NuCypher prevents unauthorized access and meets privacy, security, and compliance requirements.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483391307655{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #28b1d3;">Border Patrol for Your Data</span></h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Boundary Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This maintains data sovereignty. With NuCypher, you control not only where your data resides but who can access it, and from where. Define access controls based on geographic area, sets of nodes meeting certain compliance or regulatory requirements, or a number of other factors, to easily comply with data sovereignty requirements and protect against both insider threats and external breaches.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483391704794{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #28b1d3;">FIPS 140-2 Compliant Key Management</span></h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Military Strength Key Management</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]It is easilyintegrated into the NuCypher platform through integrations with leading Hardware Security Module vendors. Keys are managed through policy settings, making the system easy to use. NuCypher offers ultra-efficient key rotation, where administrators can set policies to re-key automatically in accordance with industry regulations like PCI or with internal guidelines.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Compliance and Data Governance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6226-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-02 21:15:01', '2017-01-02 21:15:01', '', 6226, 'http://nucypher.com/2017/01/02/6226-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
