efault"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392253036{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Fine Grained Access Control</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Role-Based Access Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This gives you the ability to maintain a separation of duties between administrative and authorized user access. NuCypher prevents unauthorized access and meets privacy, security, and compliance requirements.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392259394{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Border Patrol for Your Data</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Boundary Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This maintains data sovereignty. With NuCypher, you control not only where your data resides but who can access it, and from where. Define access controls based on geographic area, sets of nodes meeting certain compliance or regulatory requirements, or a number of other factors, to easily comply with data sovereignty requirements and protect against both insider threats and external breaches.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom