(6310, 1, '2017-01-02 21:55:52', '2017-01-02 21:55:52', '[full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]Companies are adopting Hadoop as a lower cost, higher performance alternative to proprietary data warehousing and are now using data lakes for storing both structured and unstructured data, which quite often contains sensitive information. Data being ingested and residing in the data lake needs to be accessed by different teams including business analysts, data scientists, developers, and others in the enterprise. In many cases, it also needs to be shared with partners and customers externally.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]Enforcing existing enterprise security models in this new paradigm has proven difficult because Hadoop was not designed with security in mind and the current set of alternative data encryption and tokenization products require unacceptable trade-offs between security, performance and cost. The NuCypher platform allows you to easily apply existing roles and user privileges to your data lakes, without sacrificing performance or increasing costs.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#454156" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][testimonial_slider style="default" autorotate="6500"][testimonial name="Heather Wilson, CDO of AIG, a global insurance organization" quote="My job is to create a data infrastructure so that employees can access and use all of this data  to make it available in a way that doesnt take away from them doing their jobs." id="1483386688434-7241e-3ca5" title="Testimonial" tab_id="1483392985665-3"][/testimonial][/testimonial_slider][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" text_align="left"][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#01579b" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393447012{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Multi-Tenant Administration</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0277bd" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393464100{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Revocable Access</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0288d1" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393474553{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Policy-Based Encryption</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner boxed="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#039be5" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393485314{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Separation of Duties</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393543794{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">On-Premise or In-The-Cloud: No Problem</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Multi-Tenant Administration</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher allows permissions on different data sets to be delegated to different administrators. You can extend Hadoop to more users, securely store sensitive data with non-sensitive data, and share it with users across all departments and multiple organizations through multi-tenant authorization and fine-grained access controls.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393591420{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Adds and Removes User Access in Real-Time</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Enterprise User Synchronization</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Access policies are inherited from the Hadoop management platform and tied to LDAP/AD/Kerberos to maintain real-time user provisioning and de-provisioning synchronization.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393638138{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Block Sensitive Data - Analyze Valuable Data</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Policy-Based Granular Encryption</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Control who can use data, where they can use it, and when they can use it. By sharing data with granular permissions, third parties or other departments within an organization can only decrypt the specific slices of the data (i.e. columns and fields) which they are allowed to access.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393984218{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Maintain Access Policies To Protect Against Internal Threats</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Enforce Separation of Duties</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Keep administrators and users in their swim lanes to meet compliance and governance requirements. Enforce role-based access controls (RBAC) that are granular enough to enable least privilege permissions and enforce separation of duties.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Data Sharing and Multi-Tenancy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6228-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-02 21:55:52', '2017-01-02 21:55:52', '', 6228, 'http://nucypher.com/2017/01/02/6228-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(6311, 1, '2017-01-03 22:16:42', '2017-01-03 22:16:42', '[full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]Running Hadoop in the cloud makes sense for many of the same reasons as running any other business application or platform on the cloud. It provides a tremendous opportunity to increase business efficiency, reduce costs and, most importantly, increase agility and the speed of innovation. But for most organizations moving to the cloud is a non-starter due to data governance and control issues. Beyond the need to protect data from unauthorized insider access and cyber attacks, organizations need safeguards so that even their cloud provider cant arbitrarily access data that is stored on their infrastructure.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]NuCypher provides an encryption layer with access controls embedded directly into the encryption layer. As a result, decryption permissions can be managed without access to the secret keys, allowing you to protect data in a safe and compliant manner. Privacy, confidentiality, and data integrity are maintained by encrypting the contents of stored files and allows these encrypted files to be stored on outsourced servers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section image_url="6411" bg_pos="Center Center" background_color="#01579b" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][testimonial_slider style="default" autorotate="6500"][testimonial name="Chief Technology Officer, Leading US Investment Bank" quote="We will NEVER use cloud-based key management systems. NuCyphers ability to keep secret keys on-premise along with fast and secure re-keying is a must-have for banking." id="1483386688434-7f803-6c28" title="Testimonial" tab_id="1483394375803-8"][/testimonial][/testimonial_slider][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483395327946{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Encryption And Policy That Follow The Workload</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Easy Migration From On-Premise To Cloud And Between Clouds</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="light" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" text_align="left"][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#01579b" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6437" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394558874{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Premise-Based Key Management</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0277bd" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6438" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394568555{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Automated Key Rotation</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0288d1" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6421" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483480095865{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>FIPS Compliance</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner boxed="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#039be5" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6436" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394592691{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Multi-Layer Security</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394807186{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Maintain 100% Control of Your Data - End of Story</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Premise-Based Key Management</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher is designed to enforce premise-based key management, so that keys never leave your control. It supports encryption for unlimited clusters across multiple physical locations and private, public, or hybrid clouds. Cloud providers receive only encrypted data. On-premise key management means that nobody can access your data without your consent  nobody![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6437" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6438" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394857827{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Blazingly Fast Key Rotation</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Automated Key Rotation</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Proper encryption key management is just as important as encryption itself. With NuCypher, key management is easily integrated into the Hadoop platform dashboard through APIs, and keys are managed through policy settings, making the system easy to use. NuCypher offers ultra-efficient key rotation where administrators can set policies to re-key in accordance with industry regulations like PCI or with company guidelines. This can be done automatically on a fixed schedule or an an ad-hoc basis as needed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394907139{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Meets Compliance for Finance, Healthcare, Government, and More</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">FIPS 140-2 Compliance</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher\'s Military-grade FIPS 140-2 compliant key manager helps organizations meet compliance requirements and protect private information. It allows administrators to track all key retrieval, key management, and system activity while exclusive control over the encryption keys is maintained in a Hardware Security Module in line with compliance standards.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6421" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6436" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394962162{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Data Encryption At-Rest, In-Transit, and In-Use</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Multi-Layer Security</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher offers Block-Level Encryption and also supports file encryption to secure data at-rest and in-transit. To ensure that data is protected wherever it goes while still being flexible enough to use, fine-grained field/column protection can be applied. Fine-grained encryption can continue while data is in-use and during analytical processing.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Cloud Enablement', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6230-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-01-03 22:16:42', '2017-01-03 22:16:42', '', 6230, 'http://nucypher.com/2017/01/02/6230-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
