(6314, 1, '2017-01-02 22:12:42', '2017-01-02 22:12:42', '[full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]Companies are adopting Hadoop as a lower cost, higher performance alternative to proprietary data warehousing and are now using data lakes for storing both structured and unstructured data, which quite often contains sensitive information. Data being ingested and residing in the data lake needs to be accessed by different teams including business analysts, data scientists, developers, and others in the enterprise. In many cases, it also needs to be shared with partners and customers externally.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]Enforcing existing enterprise security models in this new paradigm has proven difficult because Hadoop was not designed with security in mind and the current set of alternative data encryption and tokenization products require unacceptable trade-offs between security, performance and cost. The NuCypher platform allows you to easily apply existing roles and user privileges to your data lakes, without sacrificing performance or increasing costs.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#454156" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][testimonial_slider style="default" autorotate="6500"][testimonial name="Heather Wilson, CDO of AIG, a global insurance organization" quote="My job is to create a data infrastructure so that employees can access and use all of this data  to make it available in a way that doesnt take away from them doing their jobs." id="1483386688434-7241e-3ca5" title="Testimonial" tab_id="1483392985665-3"][/testimonial][/testimonial_slider][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="light" top_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">A Scalable Policy-Based Approach To Ensure The Right Users Have Access To The Right Data</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="light" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" text_align="left"][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#01579b" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393447012{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Multi-Tenant Administration</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0277bd" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393464100{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Revocable Access</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0288d1" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393474553{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Policy-Based Encryption</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner boxed="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#039be5" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393485314{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Separation of Duties</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393543794{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">On-Premise or In-The-Cloud: No Problem</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Multi-Tenant Administration</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher allows permissions on different data sets to be delegated to different administrators. You can extend Hadoop to more users, securely store sensitive data with non-sensitive data, and share it with users across all departments and multiple organizations through multi-tenant authorization and fine-grained access controls.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393591420{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Adds and Removes User Access in Real-Time</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Enterprise User Synchronization</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Access policies are inherited from the Hadoop management platform and tied to LDAP/AD/Kerberos to maintain real-time user provisioning and de-provisioning synchronization.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393638138{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Block Sensitive Data - Analyze Valuable Data</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Policy-Based Granular Encryption</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Control who can use data, where they can use it, and when they can use it. By sharing data with granular permissions, third parties or other departments within an organization can only decrypt the specific slices of the data (i.e. columns and fields) which they are allowed to access.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483393984218{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Maintain Access Policies To Protect Against Internal Threats</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Enforce Separation of Duties</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Keep administrators and users in their swim lanes to meet compliance and governance requirements. Enforce role-based access controls (RBAC) that are granular enough to enable least privilege permissions and enforce separation of duties.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Data Sharing and Multi-Tenancy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6228-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-02 22:12:42', '2017-01-02 22:12:42', '', 6228, 'http://nucypher.com/2017/01/02/6228-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(6315, 1, '2017-01-04 18:15:33', '2017-01-04 18:15:33', '[full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]Data governance and compliance requirements are growing in regulated industries such as healthcare, financial services, and retail due to the accelerating frequency and scope of data breaches. Big data presents tremendous challenges when it comes to maintaining regulatory compliance and adhering to data sovereignty regulations. As traditional data repositories with strictly defined compliance rules morph into data lakes filled with a mix of data, controlling access to sensitive information becomes increasingly difficult. And with more users leveraging and processing the data, it frequently gets transformed into new forms of data with varying levels of sensitivity. The totality of these activities makes it difficult to perform compliance functions when data is constantly changing, moving between locations, and being access by disparate users.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]NuCypher provides data-centric security that follows the data wherever it goes and easily integrates into your security and compliance policies to bring data lakes into compliance with corporate and regulatory data protection initiatives including GDPR, HIPAA, HITECH, and PCI. By sharing data with granular permission, third parties or other departments within an organization can only access the specific slices of data which they are allowed to decrypt, allowing you to restrict access to sensitive data while at the same time freeing the data needed to deliver business insights.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section image_url="6411" bg_pos="Center Center" background_color="#01579b" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][testimonial_slider style="default" autorotate="6500"][testimonial name=" Chief Architect at Global Financial Institution" quote="My assignment is to make the data more accessible and available, to accelerate speed to insight, yet at the same time be aware of the regulatory environment and the need for strong data governance. Other products we looked failed to address compliance requirements without significant downtime and performance constraints- NuCypher allows us to reduce our data risk and increase our business agility." id="1483382588028-2b3ff-516a" title="Testimonial" tab_id="1483386688434-7"][/testimonial][/testimonial_slider][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Leverage Existing Roles And Privileges To Easily And Consistently Manage Policies</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="light" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" text_align="left"][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#01579b" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6443" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390617043{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Encryption of Sensitive Data</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0277bd" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6441" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390762481{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Role-Based Access Control</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0288d1" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6440" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390774334{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Boundary Control</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner boxed="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#039be5" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6442" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390782689{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Key Management</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392367585{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Encryption of Sensitive Data Everywhere It Goes</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>End-to End Encryption of Sensitive Data</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]The NuCypher platform supports granular encryption, allowing fine-grained decryption permissions both for internal employees and external partners and customers. in multi-tenant cloud environments and centralized data lakes. And it works seamlessly across multi-tenant environments and centralized data lakes as well as on-premise and in private, hybrid, and public clouds.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6443" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6441" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392253036{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Fine Grained Access Control</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Role-Based Access Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This gives you the ability to maintain a separation of duties between administrative and authorized user access. NuCypher prevents unauthorized access and meets privacy, security, and compliance requirements.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392259394{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Border Patrol for Your Data</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Boundary Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This maintains data sovereignty. With NuCypher, you control not only where your data resides but who can access it, and from where. Define access controls based on geographic area, sets of nodes meeting certain compliance or regulatory requirements, or a number of other factors, to easily comply with data sovereignty requirements and protect against both insider threats and external breaches.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6440" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6442" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392266454{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">FIPS 140-2 Compliant Key Management</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Military Strength Key Management</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]It is easilyintegrated into the NuCypher platform through integrations with leading Hardware Security Module vendors. Keys are managed through policy settings, making the system easy to use. NuCypher offers ultra-efficient key rotation, where administrators can set policies to re-key automatically in accordance with industry regulations like PCI or with internal guidelines.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Compliance and Data Governance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6226-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-01-04 18:15:33', '2017-01-04 18:15:33', '', 6226, 'http://nucypher.com/2017/01/02/6226-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
