(6365, 1, '2017-01-03 02:18:27', '2017-01-03 02:18:27', '[full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]Data governance and compliance requirements are growing in regulated industries such as healthcare, financial services, and retail due to the accelerating frequency and scope of data breaches. Big data presents tremendous challenges when it comes to maintaining regulatory compliance and adhering to data sovereignty regulations. As traditional data repositories with strictly defined compliance rules morph into data lakes filled with a mix of data, controlling access to sensitive information becomes increasingly difficult. And with more users leveraging and processing the data, it frequently gets transformed into new forms of data with varying levels of sensitivity. The totality of these activities makes it difficult to perform compliance functions when data is constantly changing, moving between locations, and being access by disparate users.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]NuCypher provides data-centric security that follows the data wherever it goes and easily integrates into your security and compliance policies to bring data lakes into compliance with corporate and regulatory data protection initiatives including GDPR, HIPAA, HITECH, and PCI. By sharing data with granular permission, third parties or other departments within an organization can only access the specific slices of data which they are allowed to decrypt, allowing you to restrict access to sensitive data while at the same time freeing the data needed to deliver business insights.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#454156" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][testimonial_slider style="default" autorotate="6500"][testimonial name=" Chief Architect at Global Financial Institution" quote="My assignment is to make the data more accessible and available, to accelerate speed to insight, yet at the same time be aware of the regulatory environment and the need for strong data governance. Other products we looked failed to address compliance requirements without significant downtime and performance constraints- NuCypher allows us to reduce our data risk and increase our business agility." id="1483386688434-73837-4642" title="Testimonial" tab_id="1483409906691-8"][/testimonial][/testimonial_slider][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" text_align="left"][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#01579b" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390617043{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Encryption of Sensitive Data</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0277bd" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390762481{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Role-Based Access Control</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#0288d1" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390774334{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Boundary Control</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner boxed="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color="#039be5" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483390782689{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Key Management</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392367585{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Encryption of Sensitive Data Everywhere It Goes</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>End-to End Encryption of Sensitive Data</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]The NuCypher platform supports granular encryption, allowing fine-grained decryption permissions both for internal employees and external partners and customers. in multi-tenant cloud environments and centralized data lakes. And it works seamlessly across multi-tenant environments and centralized data lakes as well as on-premise and in private, hybrid, and public clouds.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392253036{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Fine Grained Access Control</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Role-Based Access Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This gives you the ability to maintain a separation of duties between administrative and authorized user access. NuCypher prevents unauthorized access and meets privacy, security, and compliance requirements.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392259394{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Border Patrol for Your Data</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Boundary Control</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]This maintains data sovereignty. With NuCypher, you control not only where your data resides but who can access it, and from where. Define access controls based on geographic area, sets of nodes meeting certain compliance or regulatory requirements, or a number of other factors, to easily comply with data sovereignty requirements and protect against both insider threats and external breaches.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483392266454{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">FIPS 140-2 Compliant Key Management</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Military Strength Key Management</strong></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]It is easilyintegrated into the NuCypher platform through integrations with leading Hardware Security Module vendors. Keys are managed through policy settings, making the system easy to use. NuCypher offers ultra-efficient key rotation, where administrators can set policies to re-key automatically in accordance with industry regulations like PCI or with internal guidelines.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Hadoop', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6232-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-03 02:18:27', '2017-01-03 02:18:27', '', 6232, 'http://nucypher.com/2017/01/03/6232-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(6366, 1, '2017-01-04 17:06:38', '2017-01-04 17:06:38', '[full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]NuCypher Hadoop leads the advancement of big data security with an innovative re-encryption-based data access control system for Hadoop. Purpose-built to enable the secure sharing of sensitive data in compliance with governance and residency requirements, NuCypher Hadoop arms security executives with new capabilities to stop threats faster and protect sensitive, globally distributed corporate data lakes from ever-evolving global security threats.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Store sensitive data with non-sensitive data and share it with internal and external users around the globe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Encryption policies that follow the workload  easy migration from on-premise to cloud and between clouds.</li>\r\n 	<li>Easily and consistently manage policies for user roles to enforce compliance and data governance policies.</li>\r\n 	<li>Enable data de-identification in test, development, and production.\r\nZero downtime key rotation for your Hadoop platform. No more SLA disruptions or late night downtime!</li>\r\n 	<li>Easy to use encryption key management  no more complex, confusing management tools and processes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quick time-to-value. Hadoop platform agnostic, easy installation, drop-in replacement for Transparent Data Encryption (TDE).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6538" alignment="center" anima