ed on policies: who can use the data, where they can use it, and when they can use it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text][icon enable_animation="true" color="Accent-Color" animation_speed="Medium" icon_size="60" animation_delay="" image="basic_key.svg"]<strong> Automated and Simplified Key Management Thats Blazingly Fast. </strong>NuCypher Hadoop is designed to support premise-based key management, so that keys never leave your control. NuCypher Hadoop is able to support encryption for unlimited clusters across multiple physical locations and private, public, or hybrid clouds.\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Hadoop', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6232-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-03 02:50:02', '2017-01-03 02:50:02', '', 6232, 'http://nucypher.com/2017/01/03/6232-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
