t][vc_column_text]NuCypher Hadoop supports granular encryption, allowing fine-grained decryption permissions, combined with delegated access both internally for employees and externally for partners and customers in multi-tenant cloud environments and centralized data lakes. It works seamlessly across your entire environment -- on-premise, hybrid, and public cloud -- while eliminating single points of trust, enabling enterprises to leverage the elasticity of the public cloud while maintaining on-premise key management.[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="Full Width Line" line_thickness="1" divider_color="accent-color" custom_height="32"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="0"][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-basic-lock" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Policy-Based Encryption for Total Control. </strong>NuCypher Hadoop covers everything and can protect broadly with coarse-grained file or block encryption as well as granularly by field. Set access based on policies: who can use the data, where they can use it, and when they can use it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-basic-key" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Automated and Simplified Key Management Thats Blazingly Fast. </strong>NuCypher Hadoop is designed to support premise-based key management, so that keys never leave your control. NuCypher Hadoop is able to support encryption for unlimited clusters across multiple physical locations and private, public, or hybrid clouds.\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-ecommerce-graph2" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Unparalleled Performance and Scalability With Zero Impact On Analytics.</strong>With NuCypher Hadoop, processing does\'t require communication between compute nodes and the key management services (KMS). This means the KMS doesn\'t have to stay online during a job, removing latency bottlenecks and slow requests over the network.<strong>\r\n</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-basic-gear" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Adaptable to Fit Existing Hadoop Environments.</strong>NuCypher Hadoop offers broad platform support, is Hadoop distribution agnostic and can be used with Apache Hadoop, Cloudera and Hortonworks distributions, as well as Amazon\'s EMR. It\'s a drop-in replacement for Transparent Data Encryption (TDE) with no change to user experience.\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="80" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483413670633{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Unparalleled Performance For Faster Time To Insight</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][image_with_animation image_url="6297" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#00695c" text_color="light" text_align="center" top_padding="100" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_btn size="medium" button_style="regular" button_color_2="Accent-Color" icon_family="fontawesome" url="#" text="Get The NuCypher Performance Report" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-arrow-right"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Hadoop', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6232-revision-v1', '', ''