 center;">Security</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Military-strength encryption and fine-grained policy help secure cloud and on-premise data from internal and external threats.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="padding-3-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" centered_text="true" width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[icon enable_animation="true" color="Accent-Color" animation_speed="Medium" icon_size="60" animation_delay="" image="basic_gear.svg"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Control</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ensure the right people have the right access to the right data. Fine-grained access control keeps everyone in check.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="padding-3-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" centered_text="true" width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[icon enable_animation="true" color="Accent-Color" animation_speed="Medium" icon_size="60" animation_delay="" image="ecommerce_receipt_dollar.svg"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Savings</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Reduce encryption management cost and complexity. Leverage the scalability and elasticity of cloud services and support multi-tenancy without jeopardizing security.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" full_screen_row_position="middle" bg_color="#37474f" scene_position="center" text_color="light" text_align="left" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="155" overlay_strength="0.3"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Partners</h2>\r\n[/vc_