ing_position="all" background_color="#039be5" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/4"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394592691{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h5>Multi-Layer Security</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394807186{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Maintain 100% Control of Your Data - End of Story</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Premise-Based Key Management</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher is designed to enforce premise-based key management, so that keys never leave your control. It supports encryption for unlimited clusters across multiple physical locations and private, public, or hybrid clouds. Cloud providers receive only encrypted data. On-premise key management means that nobody can access your data without your consent  nobody![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394857827{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Blazingly Fast Key Rotation</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Automated Key Rotation</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Proper encryption key management is just as important as encryption itself. With NuCypher, key management is easily integrated into the Hadoop platform dashboard through APIs, and keys are managed through policy settings, making the system easy to use. NuCypher offers ultra-efficient key rotation where administrators can set policies to re-key in accordance with industry regulations like PCI or with company guidelines. This can be done automatically on a fixed schedule or an an ad-hoc basis as needed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394907139{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Meets Compliance for Finance, Healthcare, Government, and More</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">FIPS 140-2 Compliance</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher\'s Military-grade FIPS 140-2 compliant key manager helps organizations meet compliance requirements and protect private information. It allows administrators to track all key retrieval, key management, and system activity while exclusive control over the encryption keys is maintained in a Hardware Security Module in line with compliance standards.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6299" alignment="" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483394962162{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Data Encryption At-Rest, In-Transit, and In-Use</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;">Multi-Layer Security</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher offers Block-Level Encryption and also supports file encryption to secure data at-rest and in-transit. To ensure that data is protected wherever it goes while still being flexible enough to use, fine-grained field/column protection can be applied. Fine-grained encryption can continue while data is in-use and during analytical processing.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Cloud Enablement', ''