(6539, 1, '2017-01-04 17:05:21', '2017-01-04 17:05:21', '[full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text]NuCypher Hadoop leads the advancement of big data security with an innovative re-encryption-based data access control system for Hadoop. Purpose-built to enable the secure sharing of sensitive data in compliance with governance and residency requirements, NuCypher Hadoop arms security executives with new capabilities to stop threats faster and protect sensitive, globally distributed corporate data lakes from ever-evolving global security threats.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Store sensitive data with non-sensitive data and share it with internal and external users around the globe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Encryption policies that follow the workload  easy migration from on-premise to cloud and between clouds.</li>\r\n 	<li>Easily and consistently manage policies for user roles to enforce compliance and data governance policies.</li>\r\n 	<li>Enable data de-identification in test, development, and production.\r\nZero downtime key rotation for your Hadoop platform. No more SLA disruptions or late night downtime!</li>\r\n 	<li>Easy to use encryption key management  no more complex, confusing management tools and processes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quick time-to-value. Hadoop platform agnostic, easy installation, drop-in replacement for Transparent Data Encryption (TDE).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6538" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][vc_row_inner text_align="left"][vc_column_inner column_padding="padding-10-percent" column_padding_position="left" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/2"][nectar_btn size="medium" button_style="regular" button_color_2="Accent-Color" icon_family="fontawesome" url="/try-nucypher/" text="Try NuCypher" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-arrow-right" margin_top="50" margin_bottom="20" margin_left="10"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding="padding-7-percent" column_padding_position="right" background_color_opacity="1" width="1/2"][nectar_btn size="medium" button_style="regular" button_color_2="Accent-Color" icon_family="fontawesome" url="#" text="Get the Brochure" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-arrow-right" margin_top="50" margin_bottom="20" margin_left="10"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section image_url="6400" bg_pos="Center Center" background_color="#00695c" text_color="light" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][testimonial_slider style="default" autorotate="6500"][testimonial name="Goldman Sachs" quote="There are four obstacles to public cloud in financial services. (1) Key rotation; (2) On-premise key management; (3) FIPS compliance; and (4) Intrusion protection. NuCypher addresses the first three of these, easing our adoption of cloud technology." id="1483386688434-73837-4642" title="Testimonial" tab_id="1483409906691-8"][/testimonial][/testimonial_slider][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="90" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483411195782{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Maintain 100% Control of Your Data - Always</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Multi-Layer Security for Robust Policy Enforcement and Flexibility\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>File</li>\r\n 	<li>Block</li>\r\n 	<li>Field</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPolicy-Based Encryption for Total Control\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cloud Control - block cloud providers access to data</li>\r\n 	<li>Boundary Control  enforce data sovereignty and block out of country access</li>\r\n 	<li>Data Control  broad and deep data encryption for shared data lakes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][image_with_animation image_url="6536" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="80" bottom_padding="30"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483411380408{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Make Your Data An Asset  Not A Liability</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]NuCypher Hadoop supports granular encryption, allowing fine-grained decryption permissions, combined with delegated access both internally for employees and externally for partners and customers in multi-tenant cloud environments and centralized data lakes. It works seamlessly across your entire environment -- on-premise, hybrid, and public cloud -- while eliminating single points of trust, enabling enterprises to leverage the elasticity of the public cloud while maintaining on-premise key management.[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="Full Width Line" line_thickness="1" divider_color="accent-color" custom_height="32"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="0"][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-basic-lock" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Policy-Based Encryption for Total Control. </strong>NuCypher Hadoop covers everything and can protect broadly with coarse-grained file or block encryption as well as granularly by field. Set access based on policies: who can use the data, where they can use it, and when they can use it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-basic-key" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Automated and Simplified Key Management Thats Blazingly Fast. </strong>NuCypher Hadoop is designed to support premise-based key management, so that keys never leave your control. NuCypher Hadoop is able to support encryption for unlimited clusters across multiple physical locations and private, public, or hybrid clouds.\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section text_color="dark" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-ecommerce-graph2" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Unparalleled Performance and Scalability With Zero Impact On Analytics.</strong>With NuCypher Hadoop, processing does\'t require communication between compute nodes and the key management services (KMS). This means the KMS doesn\'t have to stay online during a job, removing latency bottlenecks and slow requests over the network.<strong>\r\n</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="padding-5-percent" column_padding_position="left-right" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/2" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_icon icon_family="linea" enable_animation="true" animation_speed="medium" icon_style="border-basic" icon_border_thickness="2px" icon_color="Accent-Color" icon_padding="20px" icon_linea="icon-basic-gear" icon_size="60"][vc_column_text]<strong>Adaptable to Fit Existing Hadoop Environments.</strong>NuCypher Hadoop offers broad platform support, is Hadoop distribution agnostic and can be used with Apache Hadoop, Cloudera and Hortonworks distributions, as well as Amazon\'s EMR. It\'s a drop-in replacement for Transparent Data Encryption (TDE) with no change to user experience.\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section background_color="#ffffff" text_color="dark" top_padding="80" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/1" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483413670633{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Unparalleled Performance For Faster Time To Insight</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][image_with_animation image_url="6537" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" box_shadow="none" max_width="100%"][/vc_column][/full_width_section][full_width_section image_url="6400" background_color="#00695c" text_color="light" text_align="center" top_padding="100" bottom_padding="90"][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="2/3" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][nectar_btn size="medium" button_style="regular" button_color_2="Accent-Color" icon_family="fontawesome" url="#" text="Get The NuCypher Performance Report" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-arrow-right"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding="no-extra-padding" column_padding_position="all" background_color_opacity="1" background_hover_color_opacity="1" width="1/6" tablet_text_alignment="default" phone_text_alignment="default"][/vc_column][/full_width_section]', 'Hadoop